    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-quality 2002 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Laguna Seca Blue. This specimen is powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Vanos system that delivers a crisp, linear power delivery to an 8,000 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M-differential lock. Mechanical integrity is paramount; this vehicle has received documented rod bearing replacement and comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement. The chassis retains its factory-spec kinematics with original equipment dampers, ensuring the telepathic steering response these cars are known for. The interior showcases immaculate Nappa leather and a flawless instrument cluster. This is an investment-grade example for the discerning collector who prioritizes mechanical provenance and aesthetic perfection.",
